thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Forms Syntron Information sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 30 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Forms Syntron Information sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 30 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - shenzhen forms syntron information co ltd

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - Shenzhen Forms Syntron Information Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 15 percent to 30 percent, or to be 87.0 million yuan to 98.3 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 75.6 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is increased software development and technology maintenance income Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/c35PxW Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
